function.arguments:
{"cmd": "cd apps/floating-panel && python3 << 'EOF'
with open('src/renderer/graph.mjs', 'r') as f:
    content = f.read()

# 检查 renderGraph 函数中是否有重复的 selectorMap 构建逻辑
# 在源代码中，我添加了 selectorMap 构建逻辑，但可能与 drawAllConnections 中的重复

# 首先，移除 renderGraph 中的 selectorMap 构建逻辑，因为 drawAllConnections 中已经包含了
# 只保留 drawAllConnections 中的构建逻辑

# 从 renderGraph 中移除 selectorMap 构建
lines = content.split('\n')
new_lines = []
in_render_graph = False
skip_selector_build = False

for line in lines:
    if 'function renderGraph()' in line:
        in_render_graph = True
        new_lines.append(line)
    elif in_render_graph:
        # 检查是否是 selectorMap 构建相关行
        if 'function buildSelectorMap(domNode)' in line:
            print("Found buildSelectorMap in renderGraph, skipping...")
            skip_selector_build = True
            continue
        elif skip_selector_build and line.strip().startswith('}'):
            # 找到函数结尾，停止跳过
            skip_selector_build = False
            continue
        elif skip_selector_build:
            continue
        elif 'selectorMap.clear()' in line and 'buildSelectorMap' in ''.join(lines[lines.index(line):lines.index(line)+5]):
            print("Found selectorMap building in renderGraph, skipping...")
            # Skip the selectorMap building lines
            continue
        elif 'buildSelectorMap(domData)' in line:
            print("Found buildSelectorMap call in renderGraph, skipping...")
            continue
        elif 'Built selector map' in line:
            print("Found selector map log in renderGraph, skipping...")
            continue
        else:
            new_lines.append(line)
        
        if 'canvas.appendChild(mainGroup);' in line:
            in_render_graph = False
    else:
        new_lines.append(line)

with open('src/renderer/graph.mjs', 'w') as f:
    f.write('\n'.join(new_lines))

print("✓ 移除了 renderGraph 中的 selectorMap 构建逻辑")
EOF
"}
